2: Sam Huff, CHow acquiredThe Rangers’ seventh-round pick in the 2016 draft out of Arcadia High School in Phoenix.
He began the season not even among the top 10 prospects but burst onto the scene with big power numbers in his second season at Class-A Hickory.
ProsHe has two big-time tools that leap off the paper and grab your attention – big-time power and arm strength.
He was once one of the top prospects in baseball but never hit more than 23 homers in a season.